raw_data.title: AI/ML Engineer
raw_data.description: Develop operating software that can be used for robots, artificial intelligence programs or other artificial intelligence applications. Work closely with software engineers or data engineers and others in order to produce systems that utilize artificial intelligence. Capability to adapt operating environments based on adding data. Programming systems to look for or seek out specific conditions and respond based on those factors. Clarify their objectives to others in their team as part of their duties.
raw_data.education_and_experience_substitution: BA = Associate’s degree + two (2) years of relevant experience or four (4) years of relevant experience. MA = Bachelor’s degree + two (2) years of relevant experience or Associate’s degree + four (4) years of relevant experience or six (6) years of relevant experience. Doctorate = Master’s degree + two (2) years of relevant experience, or Bachelor’s degree + four (4) years of relevant experience or eight (8) years of relevant experience.
